name: 62/R1 COZY, SUNNY ROOM. CENTER OF BOSTON BU/BC/MIT
neighborhood_overview: BU \ BC\NORTHEASTERN UNIVERSITY \ HARVARD \ MIT. This is a beautiful, newly renovated house in the middle of Boston. It is 5 min walk distance to the MBTA public transportation, the GREEN LINE which takes you to everywhere from MIT to Harvard! There is a full option kitchen with washer/dryer inside the house! The neighborhood is very safe and surrounded by the best restaurants and venues,taverns. House is very close to TJMAX l, Marshals, Target, Star market, B fresh, and ex.s

Guest access
kitchen, living room , dining room , bathrooms

Other things to note
This place is not for everyone. This is not a hotel. There is no breakfast. This is a modest & cozy place in a prime location in the heart of Boston. You cannot beat this location. We worked extremely hard to secure this location. It is not fancy. it's an old brownstone building but it has its charm. It only has the bare necessities. People love it because it is practical and functional. U

name: RD/2 BOSTON/CARSON BEACH/JFK/UMASS/PURPLE LINE
neighborhood_overview:
My house is close to most convenient train stations and downtown Boston.
1- Uphums corner trains station - 4 minutes walking distance from house
2- JFK red line train station- 10-15 minutes walking distance from house
3- Andrew red line train station - 8-10 minutes walking distance from house
4- Boston downtown by car 10-14 minutes
5 - Boston medical center 7 minutes by car
6- Longwood Medical area 10 - 15 minutes by car
7- Northeastern university
8- UMASS Boston
9- South Bay mall, one of the biggest malls in the city. (Chain grocery store, target, old navy, best by, Marshall’s, tjmax, Homedepot...)
There is a lot of restaurants around the house on the Main Street which is working until late night, you can make food delivery or pick up for your own choice. There is Italian, Asian, Hispanic, American, Greek and Turkish Restaurants close by.
description:
Dear guest Well come to our house. The space- Big beautiful Victorian house on three floors. There are other more rooms on Airbnb. You will meet other guests in the house. On the back of the house there is a patio with picnic table for common use . Interior- Beautiful hardwood floors, warm and welcoming colors. Equipped kitchen. Room- Has queen size bed, desk, lamp, closet, comfy room... Great place for business trips, students and travelers.
